function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	actorClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(MERCHANT_SON)
	
	-- Run Lyruk off and spin up vignette
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorClone) then
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorClone, false, true)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorClone, MERCHANT_MARKER_BOSS, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(actorClone, 1.0)
	end
	Hydra.EventSend("DemonFight_Start")
end
